`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Be aware that Cypress will remove and recreate this folder on every run, so donâ€™t worry if your images disappear between runs. Also, at this point you can remove the test `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`health.spec.js`}</inlineCode>{`, because itâ€™s not needed anymore ðŸ‘`}</p>
    <p>{`The last piece will be changing your documentation to point to the auto generated pictures instead of the manual. I recommend using a table because it provides a very clear interface for the readers to visualize the pictures. This is the one I used:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
